name: I Care T-Shirt
description:
Show the Sandy Hook School community you care by purchasing this I Care T-Shirt.  All profits from the sales of these shirts will go to the Sandy Hook School Support Fund.

Free shipping within the United States.  

I encourage individuals at schools to organize and place one order together setting your school address as the shipping address.  

Note:  Posters and shirts will ship separately.  

*********************************
All orders must be placed prior to December 16th, 2013.
